snippet.textDisplay:
Loved this rendition the first time I heard! Light unplugged arrangement mainly on acoustic guitar and keys to give enough prominence to vocals and Rahat saab proving his lineage with this soulful rendition! And a beautiful cameo by Momina! (there is a natural subtle vibrato in her voice which is beautiful!) And what magical lyrics by Javed Akhtar! While I am sure the original is legendary, I am sure this will connect well with the contemporary generation and carry forward this classic for many more years! :) 
A great way to welcome the weekend I would say!
snippet.textOriginal:
